Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.64,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.63,0:01:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.81,0:01:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.36,0:02:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的真名是…\N莉莉娜?匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六話\N[派對之夜]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!快點…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜?德利安小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安外務次官在衛星被殺一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你發表一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只管自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不明白我爸爸為何而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我救不了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別介意\N只要你平安就很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道這日子終有一日會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.92,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的真名是…\N莉莉娜?匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是以前提倡和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特王族的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸他臨死前有說什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，爸爸他什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.94,0:04:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜，我有話和你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你永遠做我媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安外務次官死後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經完全無人擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星和地球圈間的溝通橋樑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，因為他是優秀的人材呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那種人才\N要為新時代而犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，蕾蒂?安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還未打算回來這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，有些事情還未辦完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你給我多一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安的女兒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會失敗很少見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，希望你批准我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在JAP點出動機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帶5部去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部那麼多嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們一有行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑影就會緊隨而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是我們的心腹大患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只是攻擊新型機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果鋼彈真的出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部機動戰士或許不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派對開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關希洛?唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聖米加勒學園的資料，取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉校手續，OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的在衛星被恐怖份子殺了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的，媒體大肆張揚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候我不知道應該說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟不是開派對的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大家都好悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不能永遠只管悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會比過去活得更堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只管哭會被爸爸責備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛轉校!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他轉來這學園還未滿一個月啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要去戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個任務在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我見過J博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會驚奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然由初次遇見之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是令我驚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏殺死我會引起騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會有麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得舉行學園節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也享受一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少直至跳完舞為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霧這麼大，沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上把機動戰士運進船艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…什麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然這麼輕易就讓敵機潛入來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒備太鬆懈了，自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙在做什麼?\N輪到他出場了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢啊!特洛瓦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.37,0:08:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何不和大家一起行動!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.94,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我趕得及表演，那就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,團長，出場了，觀眾在等我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信我的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要靜靜地不動就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本馬戲團的著名表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.03,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱薩琳的飛刀絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位慢慢欣賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!凱薩琳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要表現得有點怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則不會有趣，人偶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男孩…不懂害怕的嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.15,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是死亡呢，他在呼喚死亡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!看不見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想死嗎!?特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特…特洛瓦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!你為何不避開!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你露出野獸般的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是和那獅子一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它討厭我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為你笑會比較可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為笑對身體有益，我保證啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.61,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好!我忘記了最重要的事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，今日對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才說過，那是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，記住要笑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看\N莉莉娜小姐變得開朗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.64,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，能為她準備禮服就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我覺得\N能看見莉莉娜小姐的禮服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，我知道得太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終要死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前不想一無所知就死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你戰鬥的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在也和希洛你在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…OZ機動戰士運輸機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏被發現了嗎!?   希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徹底攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正式發表時會解釋為圍剿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗地球圈統一聯合\N的恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我不大同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然要攻擊無武器的民間設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由其他人當戰鬥指揮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼天真會令你和部下去白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能交由那種人指揮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上去完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，作戰開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，現在降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼生氣，蕾蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，出擊   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…什麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心!是敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在這裏發生戰爭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士走過來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…軍方的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在這種地方開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐!莉莉娜小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.32,0:13:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏歐，艾亞利茲，量產型確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何敵機會在這種地方!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正和敵人機動戰士交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部機動戰士的機種呢!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道，是從未見過的機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校的預言沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是那東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到會在這種地方出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉住那部所屬不明的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的艾亞利茲出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有人在破壞OZ的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中之一是特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一樣駕駛鋼彈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.60,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有其他人嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和大家見面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝!工作後的酒特別好喝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，迪歐，迪歐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，你在那裏什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼，我在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球看的月亮好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們叫那做把酒賞月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在衛星看的月亮太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直像片墓地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墓地呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.61,0:15:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種月色我能看到何時呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙不會在看月亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只管逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也能更加懂得\N享受人生就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁還有命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道也很難做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類就是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運動性能遠遠超越我們的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是飛行型!上升!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝備太重了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事啊，不要哭，快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人應該死掉較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來了!?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說鋼彈救了德利安的女兒!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是目標-莉莉娜?德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和鋼彈的駕駛員有什麼關係嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…希洛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼!!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全…全軍覆沒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我出擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校有聯絡進來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.00,0:19:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂?安，作戰中止，快回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定放過德利安的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼!?這作戰…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，有意料之外的敵人出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我們的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信傑克斯特尉也會高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思，我經常要傑克斯幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放過莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我對他的一點謝意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,替我問候傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來傳聞是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到傑克斯的親人還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙真不坦白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 這裏始終比較好住嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.34,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你是希洛吧，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.55,0:20:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.15,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，我為何要救她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人知道太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是要殺我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我!希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.29,0:21:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為何不能下手!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.94,0:21:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.92,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃避，我求你，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.81,0:22:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.81,0:22:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.81,0:22:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.81,0:22:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.31,0:22:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.81,0:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.31,0:23:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.81,0:23:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.81,0:23:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,???Just Love???
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聯合軍首腦人物
